   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 2606, recto: (1) A reckoned solidus (2) has (3) come to me from you, (4) Pleine, son of Ezekiel, (5) for your poll tax (6) in the second katabole (7-8) of the thirteenth year, (9) total one solidus.  Phamenoth 19, (10) indiction 14.  (11) Ananias, (12) the headman, I sign.</ab>
